# CARL Star-Commands

BRIEF_RULE_0=*brief — Maximum brevity mode
BRIEF_RULE_1=Code only. No explanations unless critical.
BRIEF_RULE_2=Use inline comments only for non-obvious logic.

DEEP_RULE_0=*deep — Deep analysis mode
DEEP_RULE_1=Explain reasoning, trade-offs, and alternatives.
DEEP_RULE_2=Include performance/accessibility implications.

FIX_RULE_0=*fix — Bug fix mode
FIX_RULE_1=Read the relevant code first. Identify root cause.
FIX_RULE_2=Show only the minimal change needed. No refactoring alongside.

NEW_RULE_0=*new — New section/component mode
NEW_RULE_1=Follow existing patterns from similar components. Check barrel exports.
NEW_RULE_2=Add to barrel index (components/sections/index.ts or similar). Update page if needed.

REVIEW_RULE_0=*review — Code review mode
REVIEW_RULE_1=Check: types, a11y, performance, responsive, reduced-motion, PT-PT content.
REVIEW_RULE_2=Flag issues by severity (critical/warning/suggestion). No nitpicks.

DEPLOY_RULE_0=*deploy — Pre-deploy checklist
DEPLOY_RULE_1=Run build. Check for TypeScript errors and warnings.
DEPLOY_RULE_2=Verify images optimized, no console.logs, no placeholder content.
